OL,7,FThree daughters are taking part in the
OL,8,Fin support of their father, who has .
OL,10,FDavid Wilson, from in West Yorkshire,
OL,11,Fwas recovering from blood cancer when
OL,12,Fhe was diagnosed with MND in 2020.
OL,14,FDavid, who was a keen cyclist and fell
OL,15,Frunner, is now unable to walk and has
OL,16,Flost all independent mobility in his
OL,17,Farms and hands.
