OL,7,FHis daughter Ailsa told ITV News
OL,8,FCalendar: "There's something about
OL,9,Fwatching a parent slowly vanish that
OL,10,Fyou'll just never get over.
OL,12,F"Now, with this marathon being almost
OL,13,Fdedicated to MND - it's just raised so
OL,14,Fmuch awareness."
OL,16,FDavid will be cheering on his
OL,17,Fdaughters Ailsa and Skye, who are
OL,18,Ftaking part in the 26.2 mile race, as
OL,19,Fwell as Kelly who is running the half
OL,20,Fmarathon.
