OL,7,FIt comes after he completed the first
OL,8,Fever Rob Burrow Leeds Marathon last
OL,9,Fyear - with his wife Helen pushing him
OL,10,Fin his wheelchair to the finish line.
OL,12,FDavid said: "For me it was fairly
OL,13,Feasy, I just sat back in my buggy and
OL,14,Flet the world go by.
OL,16,F"It was fantastic, so many people kept
OL,17,Ftouching me on the hand as they ran by
OL,18,F- saying well done to me and keep
OL,19,Fgoing."
