OL,7,FThe former University of Huddersfield
OL,8,Flecturer has taken part in several
OL,9,Fother fundraising challenges since his
OL,10,Fdiagnosis to raise money and awareness
OL,11,Ffor MND charities.
OL,13,FHis daughters are now taking over the
OL,14,Ffamily's efforts, hoping to raise
OL,15,Fmoney for the MND Association.
OL,17,FDavid's wife Helen told ITV News
OL,18,FCalendar: "Telling our girls that
OL,19,Ftheir dad had cancer was tough.
