OL,7,F"But telling them he's not going to
OL,8,Fsurvive the next one was one of the
OL,9,Fhardest things we've done."
OL,11,FAilsa and Skye are two of around
OL,12,F10,000 people taking part in the Rob
OL,13,FBurrow Leeds Marathon 2024.
OL,15,FThey're joined by 83-year-old Jack
OL,16,FRose - the oldest participant this
OL,17,Fyear. It will be his first ever
OL,18,Fmarathon.
